snippet.title: Accolade Trailer | Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader
snippet.description:
The echo of your fame is heard in the farthest corners of the Koronus Expanse, Lord Captain! Look what the critics say about Warhammer 40,000: Rogue Trader.
The first CRPG in Warhammer 40,000 universe is already available on PC, Mac, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series S/X. Lead your dynasty to the glory and take your rightful place in the uncharted Koronus sector!


Become the Rogue Trader:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2186680/Warhammer_40000_Rogue_Trader/
https://www.gog.com/game/warhammer_40000_rogue_trader
https://store.epicgames.com/ru/p/warhammer-40000-rogue-trader
https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/concept/10008102/
https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9p30bfhz1bkn
